question: Which genes does Cyproterone Acetate target?
cypher:
MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Cyproterone Acetate')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Cyproterone Acetate'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Cyproterone Acetate')
)
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Durvalumab')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Durvalumab'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Durvalumab')
)
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Trastuzumab Emtansine')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Trastuzumab Emtansine'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Trastuzumab Emtansine')
)
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Arsenic Trioxide')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Arsenic Trioxide'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Arsenic Trioxide')
)
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Lazertinib')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Lazertinib'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Lazertinib')
)
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 50
